Arben Bajraktaraj https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Arben_Bajraktaraj 0 Arben Bajraktaraj (born 29 January 1973) is an Albanian actor. Bajraktaraj has starred in numerous French films but also in minor roles in international movies such as, Eden Log and Sex Traffic. He has frequently portrayed Albanian crime syndicate operatives in films like Taken and Verso. He was also well known for his role as the Death Eater Antonin Dolohov in the Harry Potter films. He has worked throughout his career with numerous film directors such as Gérard Pirès, Xavier Ruiz, Tony Gatlif and Pierre Morel. Arben_Bajraktaraj ( born_29_January_1973 ) is an_Albanian_actor .
